
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>BATTLE ZONE</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Poppins,sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#000;
color:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* Background */

body::before{
content:"";
position:fixed;
top:0;
left:0;
width:100%;
height:100%;
background:
linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.55),rgba(0,0,0,.75)),
url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511512578047-dfb367046420?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80");
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
z-index:-2;
}

body::after{
content:"";
position:fixed;
width:100%;
height:100%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);
backdrop-filter:blur(2px);
z-index:-1;
}

/* Navbar */

nav{
height:80px;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:0 8%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,.45);
backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
position:fixed;
width:100%;
top:0;
}

.logo{

font-size:32px;
font-weight:800;
color:#ffb000;
letter-spacing:2px;

}

nav ul{

display:flex;
gap:30px;
list-style:none;

}

nav a{

text-decoration:none;
color:white;
font-weight:600;
transition:.3s;

}

nav a:hover{

color:#ffb000;

}

/* Hero */

.hero{

height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
text-align:center;
padding:20px;

}

.hero h1{

font-size:80px;
font-weight:800;
text-shadow:0 0 20px black;

}

.hero p{

font-size:22px;
margin:20px auto;
max-width:800px;

}

.btn{

display:inline-block;
padding:16px 40px;
margin:15px;
font-size:18px;
font-weight:bold;
border:none;
border-radius:40px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.4s;
text-decoration:none;

}

.play{

background:#ffb000;
color:black;

}

.play:hover{

transform:scale(1.1);

}

.download{

background:transparent;
border:2px solid white;
color:white;

}

.download:hover{

background:white;
color:black;

}

/* Features */

section{

padding:80px 8%;

}

.title{

text-align:center;
font-size:45px;
margin-bottom:50px;

}

.grid{

display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));
gap:30px;

}

.card{

background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
padding:30px;
border-radius:20px;
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
transition:.4s;

}

.card:hover{

transform:translateY(-10px);
background:rgba(255,176,0,.15);

}

.card h2{

margin-bottom:15px;
color:#ffb000;

}

/* Modes */

.mode{

display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
gap:30px;
justify-content:center;

}

.modebox{

width:350px;
padding:30px;
border-radius:20px;
background:#111;
text-align:center;
transition:.4s;

}

.modebox:hover{

background:#ffb000;
color:black;

}

footer{

text-align:center;
padding:30px;
background:#111;

}

@media(max-width:700px){

.hero h1{

font-size:45px;

}

.hero p{

font-size:18px;

}

nav{

padding:0 20px;

}

nav ul{

display:none;

}

}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>

<div class="logo">BATTLE ZONE</div>

<ul>

<li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Modes</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Weapons</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Leaderboard</a></li>
<li><a href="#">Settings</a></li>

</ul>

</nav>

<div class="hero">

<div>

<h1>BATTLE ZONE</h1>

<p>
Experience intense survival battles with realistic weapons, AI bots, online multiplayer, vehicles, and stunning 3D graphics.
</p>

<a href="#" class="btn play">PLAY NOW</a>

<a href="#" class="btn download">DOWNLOAD</a>

</div>

</div>

<section>

<h1 class="title">Game Features</h1>

<div class="grid">

<div class="card">
<h2>🎯 Realistic Guns</h2>
<p>Assault rifles, sniper rifles, SMGs, pistols, grenades and more.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>🤖 Smart AI Bots</h2>
<p>Play offline with intelligent bots that search, loot, and fight.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>🚗 Vehicles</h2>
<p>Drive bikes, jeeps and sports cars across the battlefield.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>🌎 Massive Map</h2>
<p>Explore forests, deserts, cities, mountains and rivers.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>🌙 Dynamic Weather</h2>
<p>Day/Night cycle, fog, rain and atmospheric lighting.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>🏆 Battle Royale</h2>
<p>Fight to become the last player standing.</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section>

<h1 class="title">Game Modes</h1>

<div class="mode">

<div class="modebox">

<h2>Offline</h2>

<p>

✔ 50 AI Bots<br>
✔ Practice Mode<br>
✔ No Internet Required

</p>

</div>

<div class="modebox">

<h2>Online</h2>

<p>

✔ Multiplayer<br>
✔ Friends Lobby<br>
✔ Ranked Match

</p>

</div>

<div class="modebox">

<h2>Training</h2>

<p>

✔ Aim Practice<br>
✔ Weapon Testing<br>
✔ Movement Tutorial

</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

© 2026 Battle Zone | Browser FPS Game

</footer>

</body>
</html>
